{"tid":1431511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權運動】示威要小心！「監測員 」網上貼相舉報：抽出亂港分子","createTime":"2019-08-08T04:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T04:28:56.000Z","uid":271434,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0e6aef9a86ee604f7be589d0d62ff8002e5e12b7","tid":1431511,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:18:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190808/59909648\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190808%2F59909648&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rKooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=b1cbcdd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190808%2F59909648&h=6bb97f85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190808/59909648</a><br />\n<br />\n香港爆發反送中逆權運動近兩個月，北京當局近日開始進行輿論導向，招募「輿情監測員 」挖掘、蒐集、整理抹黑國家形象的幕後黑手。網上更散播「國家安全機關舉報受理平台」的訊息，呼籲將「暴徒」的照片及資料提供給國家，「只要憑照片與回鄉證做校對，就可以抽出搞亂我們香港的垃圾分子！為國家盡一分力！踢走反共勢力！」據報，對防範、制止間諜行為或偵破間諜案件提供特別線索者，最高可獲50萬元人民幣（約55萬港元）的獎勵。<br />\n<br />\n去年年底，中國更新了《反間諜法》，對有損國家安全、需加以懲罰的行為擴大了定義。若境外個人或團體捏造、歪曲事實或發布有損中國國家安全的訊息，政府可以對其進行處罰。"},{"pid":"fc9be74d254ab4256b21eb8df7f74b487a654ae3","tid":1431511,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:18:33.000Z","msg":"[突發] 更新後熱門功能缺陷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431451</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e4b49fd75a09da7ccfa7572b82618ff20db49be1","tid":1431511,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:18:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d2caf2f82a1d37ca3affe84457f4042a9fbc3bc","tid":1431511,"uid":76922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RNqo2pp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRNqo2p